{"tid":1975461,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實鬼口水呢樣野既神奇之處係邊？","createTime":"2020-04-16T14:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T01:26:36.000Z","uid":2342,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88625957718d2db4696b9426806a70d26be5e702","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"成日睇IG，好多啲人玩鬼口水既片<br />\n但黎黎去去都不外乎係篤、拉、揸，捏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一個玩法玩咁多舊鬼口水，唔會厭嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家啲鬼口水仲要進化到有名，超勁<br />\n咩水牛芝士、提摩大王、玻尿酸碎糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講真係以為買緊大公司product<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好笑係啲人整完一大盆鬼口水<br />\n然後拍片吸引啲人比錢買個陣<br />\n竟然用自己既手插落盤鬼口水到玩幾下先<br />\n咁姐係人地係買緊你玩完個啲二手膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有我見到好多人都有擺格仔舖賣呢啲鬼口水<br />\n有啲仲勁到整埋網站<br />\n其實一舊鬼口水好似先賣緊$10幾蚊<br />\n究竟係點樣維本？真係有咁多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？<br />\n<br />\n鬼口水真係令我感到百思不得其解<br />\n有無人分享下呢樣野究竟係個咩玩意黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba47cf219029b5479b37867366f2fa16858f4e5","tid":1975461,"uid":158372,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"買家係小學生 商機好大㗎"},{"pid":"502e7145f2a210482adf2b7eebed5d18f449698b","tid":1975461,"uid":338238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果你係情侶檔咁做 賺得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b86bc39ab67a662f99f2d1c3ed684bd5e66564","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba47cf219029b5479b37867366f2fa16858f4e5","tid":1975461,"uid":158372,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"買家係小學生 商機好大㗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:34:23.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鬼口水真係小學生創業佳品<br />\n但我就係好疑惑，賣咁平其實頂唔頂到咁貴租<br />\n仲要勁多競爭<br />\n講緊一間格仔舖可能已經幾個格都賣緊同一樣野"},{"pid":"eaadf4ff402058d424bc180e55d24c843b9916a7","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"502e7145f2a210482adf2b7eebed5d18f449698b","tid":1975461,"uid":338238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果你係情侶檔咁做 賺得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"sis有經驗分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係回到本既話我都去做啊<br />\n其實啲賣鬼口水既賣家係咪會互買大家啲貨<br />\n我見佢地好興拍啲開箱片<br />\n但又條條片都清一色讚舊鬼口水好玩 好篤 好香 好抵<br />\n根本除左舊鬼口水唔同，條條片都無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99a1f18da936e3f7e98621a9a6af7c0754e38bf5","tid":1975461,"uid":338238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaadf4ff402058d424bc180e55d24c843b9916a7","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"502e7145f2a210482adf2b7eebed5d18f449698b","tid":1975461,"uid":338238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"如果你係情侶檔咁做 賺得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"sis有經驗分享？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係回到本既話我都去做啊<br />\n其實啲賣鬼口水既賣家係咪會互買大家啲貨<br />\n我見佢地好興拍啲開箱片<br />\n但又條條片都清一色讚舊鬼口水好玩 好篤 好香 好抵<br />\n根本除左舊鬼口水唔同，條條片都無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但見過學校一對情侶檔做過<br />\n勁撚高人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9b3b26b114b8fb323f926b8b34e457629927b5","tid":1975461,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"攞嚟打飛機一流"},{"pid":"767fccdb3560988d203955cc5dc5b7d85a009eaf","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b9b3b26b114b8fb323f926b8b34e457629927b5","tid":1975461,"uid":55096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"攞嚟打飛機一流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:46:10.000Z","msg":"屌你真係好撚有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望賣緊鬼口水個班賣家拍開箱片時<br />\n可以採納你呢個建議，拍條鬼口水劣鳩片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7874c166835df3827024bd49af466173d29ae29","tid":1975461,"uid":2342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T14:52:54.000Z","msg":"感覺上每舊鬼口水睇落都一模一樣<br />\n只係隻色，同埋個名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88c10996dd2dda672065dad1060ce666a5c206c","tid":1975461,"uid":1590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得衣樣野拎黎玩既話其實都幾污糟....<br />\n拎黎痴下key board遙控啲塵就話，<br />\n拎黎玩，痴哂隻手啲污糟野落去，玩玩下舊野就會由香變臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋舊野玩完之後有咩用，係咪dum左佢<br />\n咁舊野係咪可以自然分解，定佢同其他垃圾一樣要得好幾十年先可以分解？"},{"pid":"751432c7d8d3f5d59239b54146ed45fa2e3ae522","tid":1975461,"uid":115279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e88c10996dd2dda672065dad1060ce666a5c206c","tid":1975461,"uid":1590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c